name: 2019-jiras-created-individual

name: 2019-neha-bhosale
jql: project = Ignitia AND created >= 2019-01-01 AND created <= 2019-12-31 AND status changed by nbhosale to "dev complete"

name: 2019-qa
jql: project = Ignitia AND created >= 2019-01-01 AND created <= 2019-12-31 AND status changed by pVallakathi to "dev complete"

name: 2019-qa-dev-assigned
jql: project = GBP AND created >= 2019-01-01 AND created <= 2019-12-31 AND "Dev Assignee" is not EMPTY AND "QA Assignee" is not EMPTY AND Team in ("GBP Delta", "GBP Omega", "GBP Lambda") AND issuetype in (story, Bug) ORDER BY priority DESC, updated DESC

name: 2019-qa-dev-missing
jql: project = GBP AND created >= 2019-01-01 AND created <= 2019-12-31 AND ("Dev Assignee" is EMPTY OR "QA Assignee" is EMPTY) AND Team in ("GBP Delta", "GBP Omega", "GBP Lambda") AND issuetype in (story, Bug) ORDER BY priority DESC, updated DESC

name: 2019-reopened
jql: project = Ignitia AND created >= 2019-01-01 AND created <= 2019-12-31 AND status changed to reopened AND issuetype in (bug, ST-Bug, Story, "Support Ticket")

name: 2019-stats
jql: project = GBP AND Team in ("GBP Delta", "GBP Omega") AND issuetype in (Story, Bug, Epic, ST-Bug, Task) AND fixVersion in (versionMatch("^[0-9.]+")) AND fixVersion in (2018.1, 2018.2, 2018.3, 2018.4, 2018.5, 2018.6, 2018.7) ORDER BY priority DESC, updated DESC

name: 2019-stats-hotfixes
jql: project = GBP AND Team in ("GBP Delta", "GBP Omega", "GBP Lambda", "GBP Alpha") AND fixVersion in (versionMatch("^2019.[0-9]+.[0-9a-zA-Z.]+")) ORDER BY priority DESC, updated DESC

name: 2019-stats-support tickets
jql: project = GBP AND Team in ("GBP Delta", "GBP Omega", "GBP Lambda", "GBP Alpha") AND issuetype = "Support Ticket" AND created > 2019-01-01 AND created < 2019-12-31 ORDER BY created ASC

name: 2019-story-bugs-all
jql: project = Ignitia AND created > 2019-01-01 AND created < 2019-12-31 AND issuetype in (ST-Bug) ORDER BY status

name: 2020.1 ownershipwise
jql: project = GBP AND issuetype in (Story, Epic, Bug, Task) AND fixVersion = 2020.1 AND component is not EMPTY AND Team in ("GBP Delta", "GBP Lambda", "GBP Omega")

name: billing-service-epiclink
jql: project = GBP AND issuetype in (Story, Bug, Task) AND issueFunction in issuesInEpics("project = GBP and 'epic name' ~ 'billing service'") ORDER BY created ASC

name: Delta sprint 93 - All
jql: project = GBP AND issuetype in (Story, Task, Bug) AND Sprint = 12665 AND Team = "GBP Delta" ORDER BY issuetype DESC

name: Filter for GBP Kappa
jql: project = Ignitia AND Team = "GBP Kappa" ORDER BY Rank ASC

name: Ignitia-manual regression Part-1
jql: issueFunction in issuesInEpics("key = gbp-35381") OR issueFunction in linkedIssuesOf("key = gbp-35381")

name: Ignitia-manual regression part-2
jql: issueFunction in linkedIssuesOf("filter=75470")

name: Ignitia-manual regression part-2.1
jql: issueFunction in linkedIssuesOf("filter=75470")

name: Ignitia-manual regression part-3
jql: (issueFunction in subtasksOf("filter=75471") OR issueFunction in subtasksOf("filter=75470") OR issueFunction in subtasksOf("filter=77270")) AND issuetype = "ST-Test Case" ORDER BY TestScript

name: lambda-since-2018-10-01
jql: project = GBP AND Team = "GBP Lambda" AND created >= 2018-10-01 AND status = Resolved ORDER BY Sprint DESC

name: Omega china golive bugs
jql: project = GBP AND labels = China AND issuetype = Bug AND Team = "GBP Omega" ORDER BY priority DESC, updated DESC

name: payment_schedule_refactoring
jql: project = GBP AND labels = payment_schedule_refactoring ORDER BY Rank, priority DESC, updated DESC
